Shot at & hit in the shoulder & wing clipped, "ARGGHH!!!" she twirled about, 
nearly falling upon her knees. 

Then she turned about face her crimson optics glowing & she growled. "Damn 
them!" she brought up her rifle, powered up, aimed then fired off 5 series of 5 
rounds rapid in the direction of the Tripreds.
